{"tid":500534,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「小英做到野」台灣新例阻親支那團體搞事！","createTime":"2017-12-16T00:26:45.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-17T08:09:04.000Z","uid":29314,"like":55,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"9f68b25c636670c4386a74e1857f7e09a50dc2f4","tid":500534,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T00:26:45.000Z","msg":"台灣立法院昨三讀通過《組織犯罪防制條例》修正案。<br />\n<br />\n由於該條例被視為針對支持兩岸統一、認同中華人民共和國的台灣統一促進黨，故又戲稱為「統促黨條款」。<br />\n<br />\n條例進一步放寬對「組織犯罪」的認定標準，將現行的「持續性及牟利性」改為「持續性或牟利性」等。未來包括統促黨、愛國同心會等親中團體如再鬧事，執法機構可據本法以「組織犯罪」對他們處罰。"},{"pid":"86f0a7fefe096de1a7664d350e96ae43083ace82","tid":500534,"uid":52595,"like":0,"dislike":8,"score":-8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T00:36:00.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"fba445b272f8b4400f3ba7a7372d59d0dcdd9ada","tid":500534,"uid":37735,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T00:44:19.000Z","msg":"香港日日退步<br />\n台灣日日進步"},{"pid":"e60b87ec11dc88b2842bf1e0226159fd2389188f","tid":500534,"uid":51937,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T00:49:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>香港日日退步<br />\n台灣日日進步</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f8eb8dc425d3bc1e21d22577d8764b339c2dcf9","tid":500534,"uid":52595,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T00:55:38.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"86e4c060ac6e12ace0e3e6bf9e88b0f56674bdab","tid":500534,"uid":51937,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T02:02:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"757727cde8382397ac62873074f8cac382a3609f","tid":500534,"uid":45368,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T05:42:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>不過講真，真是好多香港人走左過台灣！<br />\n台中台北都好多香港人開店</blockquote><br />\n遲早比台灣人鬧港蝗"},{"pid":"9d569a7fc1334ef0a0a93c47f0c16e776041c746","tid":500534,"uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"